latestIgtvVideos.title: #ContestAlert with @oberoimallmumbai
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Head over to #OberoiMall and shop for Rs. 5,000/- or more from your favourite brands to win assured 2X Club UNO reward points and a chance to be one of the two lucky winners to win vouchers worth Rs 25,000/-

Additionally, You could also be one of the lucky winners to win vouchers worth Rs 3,000/- by participating in the below contest. 

To participate :

1.Follow  @oberoimallmumbai on Instagram

2.Tell about your shopping trip and how much you miss spending time at OberoiMall on your stories or you can simply comment on #OberoiMallDaycation post at  @oberoimallmumbai page. 

3.Tag me @shreyxa & your shopping partner! You can tag as many as people you wish to (the more, the merrier)

*T&C apply.

#ShopAndWin #GoodTimesAtOberoiMall

latestIgtvVideos.title: PLUM GOODNESS SKINCARE REGIME
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Dry, dull skin calls for special care and @plumgoodness has just the products for you. Made for normal to dry skin, #NewLaunch E-Luminence Simply Supple Cleansing Balm, a sulfate-free non-drying balm cleanser that leaves my skin feeling supple, soft and glowing! What’s more? It doubles up as a water-proof makeup remover too! 
The E-Luminence Nourishing Toning Water shrinks pores, soothes your skin & balances skin pH levels for hydrated & healthy skin!
And of course, there’s E-Luminence Deep Moisturizing Crème - rich day & night creme for 24-hour hydration that provides unmatched hydration and nourishment to dry skin.
3 lucky ones can get these for FREE! For which you've to:
1. Follow my handle
2. Follow @plumgoodness
3. Tag 3 friends asking them to participate (or tag more friends for brownie points) 
4. Post this Igtv video on your story tag me and @plumgoodness 
Note: GIVE AWAY CLOSED.
#PlumGoodness #dryskinbffs
